reviewText: A Tale of Two Christmases is an episode of the 1952-53 anthology series "The Doctor".  Here it is presented under the syndication title of "The Visitor".  "The Answer" is an episode of Four Star Playhouse.  They are both interesting dramas in decent prints and appear complete.
THE QUALITY OF THIS DVD WAS TERRIBLE....THE CONTRAST WAS SOO DARK YOU COULDN'T MAKE OUT THE MOVIE.CONTACTED THE VENDOR.BUT GOT NO REPLY.THANK YOU....D SIMAN
